version_description: This is a deliberate simplification to outline the basic structure and repetition but not a bad place to start I hope? I’ve heard Billy play this several times – live and recorded – and it’s never the same twice. Sometimes he throws in Dsus2 or Dsus4 and sometimes it sounds more like A or E than Am or Em. But because he’s mostly striking individual strings, it’s kinda whatever you want it to be. Play around with it and enjoy.
